Class FastNoise.Float3

java.lang.Object
squidpony.squidmath.FastNoise.Float3
Enclosing class:
FastNoise
public static class FastNoise.Float3 extends Object
Simple container class that holds 3 floats. Takes slightly less storage than an array of float[3] and may avoid array index bounds check speed penalty.
